{"tid":1048162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用FB要繳稅 烏干達上百萬人停用社群軟體","createTime":"2019-03-05T12:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T13:06:58.000Z","uid":28765,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"20ab05ed496e183857eada3d98005f64ad30ee15","tid":1048162,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/03/05/phpDifCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2FphpDifCRN.jpg&h=7320cd6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏干達政府對使用特定的網站以及行動支付，處以稅金懲罰，導致上百萬人停止使用社群軟體。圖為烏干達總統Yoweri Museveni。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕根據英國《衛報》報導，日前烏干達政府對使用特定的網站以及行動支付，處以稅金懲罰，導致上百萬人停止使用社群軟體，批評者認為這嚴重危害公民的言論自由，並將對當地網路與金融相關產業造成衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n報導顯示，烏干達政府為了降低國民對社群網站的使用，對包括Facebook、WhatsApp和Twitter在內，超過60個網路平台的用戶，徵收1天200烏干達先令的使用稅，相當於1.67元新台幣。<br />\n<br />\n對此，烏干達財政部長David Bahati宣稱，稅收是為了增加公共服務的收入，但烏干達總統Yoweri Museveni在3月交給財政部的信中，卻顯示此稅收為了處理「網路八卦」（online gossip）。<br />\n<br />\n根據烏干達通訊委員會的資料，在新稅上路3個月後，相關網路服務訂閱數銳減了250萬，OTT服務的使用者亦減少了120萬人，使用行動支付的金額也下降了近25%。由於人們不再使用這些網路服務，有些公司甚至因此被迫裁員。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，反對者批評新稅是1種限制言論自由的行為，新稅的範圍也涵蓋行動支付，這影響了許多仰賴手機匯款的烏干達人。對此律師Irene Ikomu指出，新稅並無增加政府原先預期的收入，反倒對科技和金融產業造成衝擊。<br />\n<br />\nIkomu指出，社群軟體已成為烏干達新聞與政治消息的的主要來源，使得烏干達公民更容易對國家的政治狀況提出更多的批評。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2716773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2716773&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=40bcc32e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2716773&h=27e91677\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2716773</a>"},{"pid":"da18ba19f9e148a231aa8bffa77459a9f91e4163","tid":1048162,"uid":137704,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:46:56.000Z","msg":"Uganda Forever<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac31ce1c1ccb7ae47015493b4537856465f0fcbc","tid":1048162,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"我相信呢個烏干達係假架<br />\n真正既烏干達係好有錢&quot;呢&quot;埋左係森林<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0809c1364b5db0e31eee13acf6fdbd49d0eb85","tid":1048162,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:50:01.000Z","msg":"Uganda whatever"},{"pid":"2b6a0db2d97f6f7027aeeac856a744d4c01ce667","tid":1048162,"uid":29982,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"果個係叫瓦干達（Wakanda)唔係烏干達 （Uganda)"},{"pid":"5ddbd6c373158f68c30c31545877be1d35544c70","tid":1048162,"uid":213661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"等睇道歉"},{"pid":"4d1897d0eb0dc005475b1cfb660fddd6c1f859dd","tid":1048162,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"1986年1月29日就任<br />\n做到依家"},{"pid":"148b7acf7536cffa1ee9cc31e3f82fe54b0e4f31","tid":1048162,"uid":17628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"咁黑會唔會hi污糟啲衫䄂衫領"},{"pid":"bb9481d4c8e08b5a99fdca8e9da32ae15d004f4b","tid":1048162,"uid":54824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"佢向邊個國家學嘅呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/210533_da759384528c8d07ef8165f236bc1ddf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F210533_da759384528c8d07ef8165f236bc1ddf.png&h=22ff951f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}